WEBVTT

00:00:06.538 --> 00:00:07.913
One year ago,

00:00:07.954 --> 00:00:11.829
I rented a car in Jerusalem
to go find a man I never met

00:00:11.829 --> 00:00:13.413
but who had changed my life.

00:00:13.871 --> 00:00:16.663
I didn't have a phone number
to call to say I was coming.

00:00:17.038 --> 00:00:19.121
I didn't have an exact address,

00:00:19.163 --> 00:00:22.121
but I knew his name, Abed,

00:00:22.163 --> 00:00:26.538
I knew that he lived in a town
of 15,000, Kafr Qara,

00:00:26.579 --> 00:00:31.621
and I knew that, 21 years before,
just outside this holy city,